quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Nditsuba khu ing’ining’ini olwa ikhamuukhanga."
  53,2,"Owashienywe uno shiyakora nohomba shiyakhola kano mukhwitsukhanila tawe."
  53,3,"Ne shaboolanga khubwikombi bubwe tawe."
  53,4,"Halali ni obufimbuli bwafimbulilungwa butswa."
  53,5,"Yechesibwa nende Owamaani amanji."
  53,6,"Owalongwa okhulongwa okhulayi mana nakololokha."
  53,7,"Naye ali ebuleka wa hekulu muno wekulu lia hasi."
  53,8,"Mana nasuta ehambi nende omurumwa, ne nameta khandi okhusuta ehambi."
  53,9,"Naba shinga oburambi bwa akari wetsimbeka tsibili tsiatsiyingo tsibiri nohomba ahambi muno."
  53,10,"Mana namufimbulila Omusumba wuwe kalia akayafimbula."
  53,11,"Omwoyo shikwaboola obubeyi khukakwalola tawe."
  53,12,"Koo, mumuyingasinjia khukayalola?"
  53,13,"Mana toto (Omurumwa) yamulolakhwo (Jibril) khandi."
  53,14,"Mushisina shio musaala (mkunazi) kwokhumalilikha muno (omusala kuno kuli mwikulu lia msafu)."
  53,15,"Ahambi nende omusaala oko, kuliwo omukunda kwomwikulu kwamenywamwo."
  53,16,"Olwa kwafimbwa omusaala oko (khubunyali bwa Nyasaye) nende shiakufiimba (shilamanyishe mbu ni shina halali Nyasaye butswa niumanile)."
  53,17,"Tsimoni shitsiesundukha tawe nohomba shitsiabura eshichelo tawe."
  53,18,"Toto yalola khubimanyisio ebikhongo bia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  53,19,"Koo, mwalolakhwo Laata nende Uzza?"
  53,20,"Nende Manata, owundi wakhataru?"
  53,21,"Koo, nenywe muli nabasiani Naye ali nabakhaana?"
  53,22,"Toto okho ni okhukaba okhubi muno."
  53,23,"Ako namerasa kamwakulikha enywe nende basenywe, Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi khumeera ako tawe. Balondangasa amaparo nende shie mioyo chiabu chienya. Ne toto obulunjifu bwabetsela okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  53,24,"Mbu Omundu anyoolanga shia yekombanga?"
  53,25,"Nyasaye sa niye mwene mwikulu nende eshialo."
  53,26,"Ne ni Abamalaika benga bali mwikulu, abokhusabila khwabu shikhulikhoonya yesiyesi tawe, halali khuwa Nyasaye achamile mana namufuchilila?"